{"tid":698516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被指邀15歲女生到家私影兼性交 休班警脫罪","createTime":"2018-06-11T18:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T00:47:26.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"65b0b41075ad6985e7aa15549449ef68e10801d5","tid":698516,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T18:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/022040_a89bebeeb7d979bd95f566ca53e824aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F022040_a89bebeeb7d979bd95f566ca53e824aa.png&h=e922edfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告陳健敏(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n休班警員涉自稱攝影師邀請15歲中學女生到其家中私影，要求對方穿性感衣服，其間更疑跟她性交。休班警被控與十六歲以下女子非法性交罪，惟經審訊後裁判官指事主對案發日子說法與其他證供有出入，基於疑點利益歸於被告，裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n38歲男警陳健敏，被控於13年1月至11月28日某日，與當時15歲女童X非法性交。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指，被告否認控罪，控方需證明兩人確實在13年11月28日前性交。但案中女童X作供聲稱案發時正值暑假，又指當年就讀中四決定輟學轉做侍應，因此清晰記得是在暑假於手臂紋上紋身。惟控方傳召紋身師，根據其手機及facebook記錄，女童X是在10月18日才紋上圖案。裁判官相信紋身師是可靠證人。<br />\n<br />\n由於紋身師傅的作供與女童X的口供在時間上出現差異，基於疑點利益歸於被告下，裁定男警罪脫。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：TMCC112/18】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58304654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58304654&d=4SVUfAwZUVteQo%2F0z4mZtfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=7c616a90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58304654&h=ed5c0596\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58304654</a>"},{"pid":"a5a116318040ccf8f0e62c576ef1c4547f820102","tid":698516,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T18:21:45.000Z","msg":"逼害猶差"},{"pid":"ca6ffc936063b7c4d92584b2d90c08c7a41ecf2b","tid":698516,"uid":136707,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T19:19:27.000Z","msg":"阿sir姦細路女唔洗你教<im